<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>As a Shadow knight i must disagree. In the dungeons this is usefull. Especially when you cant waste the whole dungeon by yourself. The chances are the monster who got away will :<BR>
1) regen.<BR>
